<h1 align="center">TypeScript API Utils</h1>

<p align="center">
	Utility functions for working with TypeScript's API.
	Successor to the wonderful <a href="https://github.com/ajafff/tsutils">tsutils</a>.
</p>

<p align="center">
	<a href="#contributors" target="_blank">
