## Usage

```shell
npm i ts-api-utils
```

```ts
import * as tsutils from "ts-api-utils";
```

### API

`ts-api-utils` provides many utility functions.
Check out our API docs for details:

ğŸ“ [ts-api-utils API docs](https://joshuakgoldberg.github.io/ts-api-utils).

